abstract: SA2 based data for Non-School Qualification: Field of Study by Age by Sex, for 2011 Census. Count of persons aged 15 years and over with a qualification on Census night based on place of usual residence. Excludes persons with a qualification out of the scope of the Australian Standard Classification of Education (ASCED). Data sourced from: http://www.abs.gov.au/census. For further information about these and related statistics, contact the National Information and Referral Services on 1300 135 070. Periodicity: 5-Yearly.
